'''Mondrak''' was an exotic-looking, [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoid]] [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] magician who served as [[Gatekeeper/Legends|Gatekeeper]] to [[Krova (Hutt)|Krova]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt's]] [[Sith holocron/Legends|Sith holocron]]. Although she claimed to be the "Judge of the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]]", she was unable to break Krova's mind.<ref name="THH">{{GamerCite|5|The Hutt Hit}}</ref>

